5
00:01:19,163 --> 00:01:20,538
How do I look?

6
00:01:20,748 --> 00:01:22,207
Perfect.

7
00:01:22,458 --> 00:01:24,125
Is my hair okay?

8
00:01:24,585 --> 00:01:25,752
It's great.

9
00:01:26,003 --> 00:01:28,046
You're not even looking at it.

10
00:01:29,257 --> 00:01:30,715
It's beautiful.

11
00:01:31,175 --> 00:01:32,842
You always look beautiful.

12
00:01:33,344 --> 00:01:35,387
Did you give Roz the phone
