33
00:02:49,378 --> 00:02:53,131
- Victor, lllona.
VICTOR: Bill, Alice.

34
00:02:53,341 --> 00:02:55,884
VICTOR: Merry Christmas.
ILLONA: Thank you for coming.

35
00:02:56,260 --> 00:03:00,722
- Thanks so much for coming.
- We wouldn't miss it for the world.

36
00:03:00,931 --> 00:03:04,017
Alice, look at you.
God, you're absolutely stunning!

37
00:03:04,226 --> 00:03:06,144
