looking at his bill.

42
00:03:17,823 --> 00:03:20,241
Go inside, have a drink,
enjoy the party.

43
00:03:20,451 --> 00:03:23,161
I'll see you in a little bit.
Thanks for coming.

44
00:03:36,133 --> 00:03:38,176
Do you know anyone here?

45
00:03:39,512 --> 00:03:42,013
BILL:
Not a soul.

46
00:03:49,939 --> 00:03:54,317
Why do you think Ziegler invites us
to these things every year?

47
00:03:55,528 --> 00:03:59,989
This is what you get
for making house calls.

48
00:04:11,127 --> 00:04:13,294
You see that guy at the piano?

49
00:04:14,505 --> 00:04:17,048
I went to medical school with him.

50
00:04:17,591 --> 00:04:18,591
Really?

51
00:04:21,887 --> 00:04:24,389
He plays pretty good for a doctor.

52
00:04:25,182 --> 00:04:28,768
He's not a doctor. He dropped out.

53
00:04:31,897 --> 00:04:34,315
Ladies and gentlemen,
I hope you're enjoying yourselves.

54
00:04:34,525 --> 00:04:37,986
